nodes.text: The Numidian Prime strike team was a strike team assembled to find the notorious bounty hunter Shenda Mol. Eventually the Jedi tracked her to Numidian Prime, where she had a stronghold and a handful of followers. Jedi Master Dooku and Padawan Qui-Gon Jinn were part of the strike team, and the pair eventually captured Mol after she had tried to kill Jinn.
